<h2>Property Listing Update Required</h2>

<p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for submitting your property listing. Unfortunately, after review by our moderation team, we were unable to approve it at this time.</p>

<div class="error-box">
  <p><strong>❌ Your property listing requires changes</strong></p>
</div>

<div class="property-card">
  <h3>{{propertyTitle}}</h3>
  <p class="address">📍 {{propertyAddress}}</p>
</div>

<p><strong>Reason for rejection:</strong></p>
<div class="warning-box">
  <p>{{rejectionReason}}</p>
</div>

<p><strong>What can you do?</strong></p>
<ul style="padding-left: 20px; line-height: 2;">
  <li>Review the reason above carefully</li>
  <li>Edit your listing to address the concerns</li>
  <li>Submit your property for review again</li>
</ul>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <a href="{{editPropertyUrl}}" class="btn-primary">Edit Your Listing</a>
</div>

<p>If you believe this decision was made in error or have questions, please contact our support team.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br><strong>The Immobilier.ch Team</strong></p>
